title: Taylor Swift
description: Taylor Swift has gone from country music star to mega star! Her second album, Fearless, debuted at #1 on the Billboard 200 and won the award for Album of the Year at the Country Music Awards. Plus, Taylor has tons of cross-genre she performed on Saturday Night Live, appeared on the covers of magazines like Rolling Stone and Teen Vogue, and acted in hit movies like Hannah The Movie. Our newly revised and expanded version of Taylor Country?s Sweetheart features up-to-date information, photos, and a gorgeous new cover!
author: Ronny Bloom
